			<h2>
				<a href="http://sweatnspice.com/reviews/hot-sauce-review-sweat-%e2%80%98n-spice-presents-the-heat-seat-ep-8-red-bandit-red-bell-pepper-habanero-hot-sauce" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent link to Hot Sauce Reviews: Sweat ‘N Spice presents The Heat Seat Ep. 8 Red Bandit Red Bell Pepper Habanero Hot Sauce">
				Hot Sauce Reviews: Sweat ‘N Spice presents The Heat Seat Ep. 8 Red Bandit Red Bell Pepper Habanero Hot Sauce</a>
			</h2>
			</div>
			
			<div class="post-footer">
			<h4>
				<span class="post-date">April 16th, 2010</span>
				<span class="post-comments"><a href="http://sweatnspice.com/reviews/hot-sauce-review-sweat-%e2%80%98n-spice-presents-the-heat-seat-ep-8-red-bandit-red-bell-pepper-habanero-hot-sauce#comments" title="See comments for this post">
				Write Comment</a></span>
				<span class="post-category"><a href="http://sweatnspice.com/category/reviews" title="View all posts in Reviews" rel="category tag">Reviews</a></span>
			</h4>
			</div>
			
			<div class="post-content">
                                								<div class="postavatar">
								<img src="http://sweatnspice.com//wp-content/plugins/post-avatar/images/tongueburner.gif" width="60" height="81" alt="hot-sauce-reviews-sweat-%e2%80%98n-spice-presents-the-heat-seat-ep-8-red-bandit-red-bell-pepper-habanero-hot-sauce" />
<br />
                                <span class="author">Posted By:<br />TongueBurner</span></div>
                                			<p>Hot sauce reviewer Jordan Lee is back with the eighth episode of &#8220;The Heat Seat,&#8221; the Sweat &#8216;N Spice.com-sponsored vodcast. For his latest hot sauce review, Jordan downs some <a href="http://sweatnspice.com/products-page/all-hot-sauces/green-bandit-red-bell-pepper-habanero-hot-sauce" target="_blank">Red Bandit Red Bell Pepper Habanero Hot Sauce</a>, which he finds to be a mouthful in more ways than one.</p>
<p>See what Jordan thinks about the packaging, the color and the flavor of this red sauce from the Green Bandit company by watching the latest episode of &#8220;The Heat Seat&#8221; below.</p>
<p><object width="400" height="250"><param name="movie" value="http://www.youtube.com/v/VUco0lAadg8&#038;hl=en_US&#038;fs=1&#038;"></param><param name="allowFullScreen" value="true"></param><param name="allowscriptaccess" value="always"></param><embed src="http://www.youtube.com/v/VUco0lAadg8&#038;hl=en_US&#038;fs=1&#038;" type="application/x-shockwave-flash" allowscriptaccess="always" allowfullscreen="true" width="400" height="250"></embed></object></p>
<p><a onclick="javascript:pageTracker._trackPageview('/outgoing/www.youtube.com/watch?v=VUco0lAadg8');"  href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VUco0lAadg8" target="_blank">Hot sauce!</a></p>
<p>See <a href="http://sweatnspice.com/the-heat-seat" target="_blank">more episodes of &#8220;The Heat Seat&#8221; here</a>.</p>
